\"Italic\\\"], \\\"\[Mu]\\\"]\\)\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\()\\), \
\\(1/2\\)]\\)\"", TraditionalForm]}}},
  TicksStyle->Directive[
    GrayLevel[0], 
    Thickness[Large]]]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.8105623286627584`*^9, 3.810562477476654*^9, 3.920648130877716*^9, 
   3.9206481793208776`*^9, {3.92064833096681*^9, 3.920648335978775*^9}},
 CellLabel->"Out[96]=",ExpressionUUID->"c1eaeb21-a973-f04f-8b91-faeef74165a8"]
}, {2}]],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Figure 13.4",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ". The solutions to the quantum mechanical Morse potential (black curve), \
plotting the absolute square of the wavefunction, ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"\[RightBracketingBar]", 
    RowBox[{"\[Psi]", "(", "x", ")"}], 
    SuperscriptBox["\[LeftBracketingBar]", "2"]}], TraditionalForm]],
  ExpressionUUID->"0836e3ce-d6f8-f645-b99a-f57dc1e10ed6"],
 ", in blue. The energy eigenvalues are marked with gray lines, and the \
harmonic approximation potential is shown as a dashed black line."
}], "Affiliation",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.809435027311596*^9, 3.8094350763900714`*^9}, {
  3.80943583474421*^9, 3.8094358359299717`*^9}, {3.8094472165104203`*^9, 
  3.809447281165168*^9}, {3.809510876137825*^9, 3.809510907739876*^9}, {
  3.809968073566992*^9, 3.8099681536568317`*^9}, {3.810557260250428*^9, 
  3.8105572606139913`*^9}, {3.810568744142911*^9, 3.810568814895481*^9}, {
  3.9206485694179354`*^9, 3.9206485715849676`*^9}, {3.9399012544815044`*^9, 
  3.9399012545858135`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"712a46b3-097a-6c49-9e09-\
f04185cf094f"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Light-Matter Interactions and Perturbation Theory", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8153306013251953`*^9, 
  3.8153306090764575`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c95ff691-0fba-4e0b-be45-\
28f180a56d40"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Introduction to Time-Dependent Perturbation", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.81537781247439*^9, 3.815377843871893*^9}, {
  3.815377883181856*^9, 
  3.815377975809704*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"48eabd46-214d-4c80-ab55-\
5129729a5c78"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Up to this point, we haven\[CloseCurlyQuote]t really worked very much with \
the evolution of a system in time, but we now want to look at the ",
 StyleBox["change",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " in a system (molecule) upon its interaction with light, for which we will \
need some form of time-dependent formalism. First, recall from our discussion \
of the fifth postulate of quantum mechanics that the wavefunction of an \
unperturbed system in an eigenstate ",
 StyleBox["j",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " changes in time only by a \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]phase factor\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] given by an oscillatory complex exponential,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8153779817184505`*^9, 3.815378103494567*^9}, {
  3.8153783273242135`*^9, 3.8153784967222977`*^9}, {3.8153785944541492`*^9, 
  3.815378607902829*^9}, {3.8154775970084224`*^9, 3.8154775982885437`*^9}, {
  3.939901923244627*^9, 
  3.939901924526966*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7dacc761-453d-4852-9f0f-\
32ad20826d22"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
       StyleBox["j",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      StyleBox[
       RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
       FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], 
   StyleBox["=",
    FontSlant->"Plain"], 
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     StyleBox["\[ExponentialE]",
      FontSlant->"Plain"], 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"-", 
       SubscriptBox[
        StyleBox[
         RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", 
          StyleBox["E",
           FontSlant->"Italic"]}]], 
        StyleBox["j",
         FontSlant->"Italic"]]}], 
      RowBox[{
       StyleBox["t",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       StyleBox["/",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], "\[HBar]"}]}]], "|", 
    SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
     StyleBox["j",
      FontSlant->"Italic"]]}]}], 
  "\[RightAngleBracket]"}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
  3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
  3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8080655103101*^9, 3.808065549470801*^9}, {
  3.8080655874181037`*^9, 3.8080655997397223`*^9}, {3.80806586302172*^9, 
  3.808065882866931*^9}, {3.8080659492793603`*^9, 3.808065953047598*^9}, {
  3.808066005614772*^9, 3.8080660274348636`*^9}, {3.8080662251299095`*^9, 
  3.8080662851171017`*^9}, {3.815378518820794*^9, 3.815378562596084*^9}, {
  3.81537861215761*^9, 3.815378656577838*^9}, {3.815379235992326*^9, 
  3.815379237398435*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"424443e3-1d58-48a6-9790-\
0e3ff52efd93"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Note that the ket on the left-hand-side has a time dependence, whereas the \
one on the right-hand-side does not. What if our system is not in an energy \
eigenstate? Then we can instead write the time-dependent wavefunction of the \
system as a linear combination of the energy eigenstates, which we will label \
as",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"\[LeftBracketingBar]", 
    StyleBox["n",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
   3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
   3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8080655103101*^9, 3.808065549470801*^9}, {
   3.8080655874181037`*^9, 3.8080655997397223`*^9}, {3.80806586302172*^9, 
   3.808065882866931*^9}, {3.8080659492793603`*^9, 3.808065953047598*^9}, {
   3.808066005614772*^9, 3.8080660274348636`*^9}, {3.8080662251299095`*^9, 
   3.8080662851171017`*^9}, {3.815378518820794*^9, 3.815378562596084*^9}, {
   3.81537861215761*^9, 3.815378656577838*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "81266dfc-2624-4e58-90a7-687e171382f4"],
 " for simplicity,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8153786622423124`*^9, 3.8153786956138396`*^9}, {
  3.815378754814275*^9, 3.815378819233637*^9}, {3.8153789164881797`*^9, 
  3.8153789348918295`*^9}, {3.8153789720873957`*^9, 
  3.8153790178433056`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"712a25e9-9509-4b2f-9c77-\
ba6a34cfee09"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"|", 
     RowBox[{"\[Psi]", 
      StyleBox[
       RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
       FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], 
   StyleBox["=",
    FontSlant->"Plain"], 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     UnderscriptBox["\[Sum]", 
      StyleBox["n",
       FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
     RowBox[{
      SubscriptBox[
       StyleBox["c",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], 
       StyleBox["n",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       StyleBox["t",
        FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}], 
      SuperscriptBox[
       StyleBox["\[ExponentialE]",
        FontSlant->"Plain"], 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", 
         SubscriptBox[
          StyleBox[
           RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", 
            StyleBox["E",
             FontSlant->"Italic"]}]], 
          StyleBox["n",
           FontSlant->"Italic"]]}], 
        RowBox[{
         StyleBox["t",
          FontSlant->"Italic"], 
         StyleBox["/",
          FontSlant->"Italic"], "\[HBar]"}]}]]}]}], "|", 
    StyleBox["n",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], 
  "\[RightAngleBracket]"}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
  3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
  3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8080655103101*^9, 3.808065549470801*^9}, {
  3.8080655874181037`*^9, 3.8080655997397223`*^9}, {3.80806586302172*^9, 
  3.808065882866931*^9}, {3.8080659492793603`*^9, 3.808065953047598*^9}, {
  3.808066005614772*^9, 3.8080660274348636`*^9}, {3.8080662251299095`*^9, 
  3.8080662851171017`*^9}, {3.815378518820794*^9, 3.815378562596084*^9}, {
  3.81537861215761*^9, 3.815378656577838*^9}, {3.815379033614147*^9, 
  3.8153790773392897`*^9}, {3.8153792393653684`*^9, 3.81537924024451*^9}, {
  3.8153793909369802`*^9, 
  3.81537943105853*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"91418e62-9981-447b-8d73-\
14d4a2f2e226"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "where the coefficients ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["c",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["n",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["t",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
   3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
   3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8080655103101*^9, 3.808065549470801*^9}, {
   3.8080655874181037`*^9, 3.8080655997397223`*^9}, {3.80806586302172*^9, 
   3.808065882866931*^9}, {3.8080659492793603`*^9, 3.808065953047598*^9}, {
   3.808066005614772*^9, 3.8080660274348636`*^9}, {3.8080662251299095`*^9, 
   3.8080662851171017`*^9}, {3.815378518820794*^9, 3.815378562596084*^9}, {
   3.81537861215761*^9, 3.815378656577838*^9}, {3.815379033614147*^9, 
   3.8153790773392897`*^9}, {3.8153792393653684`*^9, 3.81537924024451*^9}, {
   3.8153793909369802`*^9, 3.81537943105853*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "6c1ade7d-a605-49e8-9dee-bbb9530ce654"],
 "give the contribution of each basis eigenfunction in time (along with the \
exponential factor). The square of the coefficients ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["c",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["n",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
   RowBox[{"(", 
    StyleBox["t",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
   3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
   3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8080655103101*^9, 3.808065549470801*^9}, {
   3.8080655874181037`*^9, 3.8080655997397223`*^9}, {3.80806586302172*^9, 
   3.808065882866931*^9}, {3.8080659492793603`*^9, 3.808065953047598*^9}, {
   3.808066005614772*^9, 3.8080660274348636`*^9}, {3.8080662251299095`*^9, 
   3.8080662851171017`*^9}, {3.815378518820794*^9, 3.815378562596084*^9}, {
   3.81537861215761*^9, 3.815378656577838*^9}, {3.815379033614147*^9, 
   3.8153790773392897`*^9}, {3.8153792393653684`*^9, 3.81537924024451*^9}, {
   3.8153793909369802`*^9, 3.81537943105853*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "c68fe0fd-acac-4d10-8528-7c1170d8e0e4"],
 "will give us the probability that the system is in state \
\[LeftBracketingBar]",
 StyleBox["n",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\[RightAngleBracket] at time ",
 StyleBox["t",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ".  "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.815379164718523*^9, 3.8153791958072705`*^9}, {
  3.8153794388361406`*^9, 3.815379501748596*^9}, {3.815379807971365*^9, 
  3.8153798150180764`*^9}, {3.8153802074798927`*^9, 
  3.815380304134411*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e937387f-c902-46da-836e-\
9809d84b8c5c"],

Cell["\<\
Remember that the wavefunction |\[Psi] (t)\[RightAngleBracket] is a solution \
to the time-dependent Schr\[ODoubleDot]dinger equation,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8153803069128065`*^9, 3.8153803184047294`*^9}, {
  3.846766066993519*^9, 
  3.8467660700484858`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"98d84edd-938c-457b-83e0-\
5083562b37bf"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]\[HBar]", " ", 
      StyleBox[
       FractionBox[
        StyleBox["\[PartialD]",
         FontSlant->"Plain"], 
        RowBox[{
         StyleBox["\[PartialD]",
          FontSlant->"Plain"], "t"}]],
       FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "|", 
     RowBox[{"\[Psi]", 
      StyleBox[
       RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
       FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}], "\[RightAngleBracket]"}], "=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["H",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
     StyleBox[" ",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], 
     StyleBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}], 
    StyleBox["|",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    RowBox[{"\[Psi]", 
     StyleBox[
      RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
      FontSlant->"Italic"]}]}]}], 
  "\[RightAngleBracket]"}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
  3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
  3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8153792281590304`*^9, 3.8153792296993537`*^9}, {
  3.815379281402275*^9, 3.815379316737402*^9}, {3.8153799308332453`*^9, 
  3.8153799333033557`*^9}, {3.815468691093717*^9, 
  3.8154686935336123`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"581e50dd-59ae-4c01-9aef-\
0dc8450b841c"],

Cell["\<\
Let us now separate the Hamiltonian operator into time-independent and \
time-dependent components in a perturbation formulation,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.815379842827999*^9, 3.815379905413232*^9}, {
  3.8153800494767733`*^9, 
  3.815380055342676*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1cde66fa-4f61-457d-8939-\
39190111aee8"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   OverscriptBox[
    StyleBox["H",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
   StyleBox[" ",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   StyleBox[
    RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
    FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "+", 
   RowBox[{
    SuperscriptBox[
     OverscriptBox[
      StyleBox["H",
       FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
     RowBox[{"(", "1", ")"}]], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     StyleBox["t",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
  3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
  3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8153792281590304`*^9, 3.8153792296993537`*^9}, {
  3.815379281402275*^9, 3.815379316737402*^9}, {3.8153799115949154`*^9, 
  3.8153799654068594`*^9}, {3.815734547252193*^9, 
  3.8157345551822777`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d44c3bef-6a4e-433e-9869-\
1aa9b0eb6db8"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Because we are interested in the interaction of the system with light, \
which is just an oscillating electromagnetic potential, we can label the \
time-dependent component as ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"V", "(", 
    StyleBox["t",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "55c483d9-106b-480a-809f-c4a798654328"],
 ","
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.815379986062453*^9, 3.8153801111464353`*^9}, {
  3.815380341689233*^9, 3.8153803424335213`*^9}, {3.815380504783449*^9, 
  3.815380505056096*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3f1f8451-c4e6-4522-be33-\
c722c4dab78e"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   OverscriptBox[
    StyleBox["H",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
   StyleBox[" ",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], 
   StyleBox[
    RowBox[{"(", "t", ")"}],
    FontSlant->"Italic"]}], "=", 
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox[
    OverscriptBox[
     StyleBox["H",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], "^"], 
    RowBox[{"(", "0", ")"}]], "+", 
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["V",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    RowBox[{"(", 
     StyleBox["t",
      FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}]}]}]}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8079712935412436`*^9, 3.8079714900326514`*^9}, {
  3.8080650361338077`*^9, 3.808065078586836*^9}, {3.8080651294863386`*^9, 
  3.8080651662446632`*^9}, {3.8153792281590304`*^9, 3.8153792296993537`*^9}, {
  3.815379281402275*^9, 3.815379316737402*^9}, {3.8153799115949154`*^9, 
  3.8153799654068594`*^9}, {3.8153800814929256`*^9, 3.8153800902783875`*^9}, {
  3.8153805007134113`*^9, 3.8153805011092744`*^9}, {3.815734561063938*^9, 
  3.8157345643450174`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a7a4d79e-1d40-4300-94b5-\
e7e6a60b7264"],

Cell["\<\
Substituting equations (20) and (23) in the time-dependent \
Schr\[ODoubleDot]dinger equation, we obtain\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.815476949787305*^9, 3.8154769645063796`*^9}, {
  3.939902363579405*^9, 3.9399023777493*^9}, {3.9399024209059715`*^9, 
  3.939902421037733*^9}, {3.9399024705866985`*^9, 
  3.939902472198326*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"96508e77-6954-49d8-b662-\
980a36314a83"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      UnderscriptBox["\[Sum]", 
       StyleBox["n",
        FontSlant->"Italic"]], 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"(", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]\[HBar]", 
          StyleBox[
           FractionBox[
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{
              StyleBox["\[PartialD]",
               FontSlant->"Plain"], 
              SubscriptBox["c", 
               StyleBox["n",
                FontSlant->"Italic"]]}], 
             RowBox[{"(", 
              StyleBox["t",
               FontSlant->"Italic"], ")"}]}], 
            RowBox[{
             StyleBox["\[PartialD]",
