Cell[TextData[{
 "Note that the potential depends not only on time but also on position and \
orientation, which will be very important later on. For now, let\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s think only about the time portion. For the system in \
starting state |",
 StyleBox["k",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "\[RightAngleBracket], using our first-order approximation for the weighting \
coefficients, we obtain"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.815482553182288*^9, 3.815482623369748*^9}, {
  3.815482822023904*^9, 
