Cell[TextData[{
 "where the sets of quantum numbers, ",
 StyleBox["J",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
 StyleBox["M",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " and ",
 StyleBox["J\[CloseCurlyQuote]",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", ",
 StyleBox["M\[CloseCurlyQuote]",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " specify the initial and final states of the system, respectively. \
Integration in spherical coordinates yields"
