Cell["\<\
We\[CloseCurlyQuote]ve already discussed the properties of the rotational \
spectra of rigid rotors, but we\[CloseCurlyQuote]ll review them again here \
briefly. The energy eigenvalues of a rigid rotor are given by\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8159222958483486`*^9, 3.815922416567474*^9}, {
