 " in ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["cm", 
    RowBox[{"-", "1"}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "519d503c-bb1e-4b22-960c-0d5b59d395fc"],
 ". Because absorption of a photon can only yield a transition from state ",
 StyleBox["J",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " to state ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"J", "+", "1"}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9cfdec09-2ae0-4c2f-a826-1f844c5121ab"],
 ", the distribution of spectral lines depends upon the initial population \
distribution, which is in turn given by the temperature. A model rotational \
spectrum of an idealized rigid rotor is shown in Figure 13.6."
}], "Text",
