bd02b0444815"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "The inversion, or reflection through center of symmetry, operation is \
similar to the reflection through a plane, but now the reflection is through \
a single point known as the inversion center ",
 StyleBox["i",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ". Inversion centers for ethane and benzene are shown in Figure 13.12"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8162575673093195`*^9, 3.8162576273436756`*^9}, {
   3.8162581228104887`*^9, 3.816258141236824*^9}, 3.9398953449074936`*^9, {
   3.9400904860801544`*^9, 
   3.9400904863178825`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a87f0230-c8fd-474a-a1e5-\
c3ef536171d8"],

